701
00:43:05,020 --> 00:43:06,940
=The Lead=
(Preview)

702
00:43:09,110 --> 00:43:12,400
Four old men and one little girl

703
00:43:12,400 --> 00:43:17,230
brought the troupe back to life with ease!

704
00:43:17,320 --> 00:43:19,800
With Hua Caixiang, at least
I had a chance to compete.

705
00:43:19,840 --> 00:43:22,280
But with you, I don't even
have the chance to compete.

706
00:43:22,280 --> 00:43:23,510
We wanna be your apprentices!

707
00:43:23,510 --> 00:43:25,230
Masters, please take us in!

708
00:43:25,360 --> 00:43:26,280
Stop fooling around!

709
00:43:26,280 --> 00:43:27,130
Get lost!

710
00:43:27,130 --> 00:43:28,630
This is so unfair!

711
